Poor Database Viewer powered by Sinatra+Haml+Sequel

Require:
  Ruby
  Gems:
    sinatra
    haml
    sequel
    (and database adatpers)

1) Setting
  $ cp config.sample.yml config.yml
  $ vi config.yml

2-a) Run application.rb with WEBrick
  $ ruby application.rb

2-b) Run as CGI
  Edit configuration file of httpd server (e.g. /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf)
  and restart httpd server.
